plyTime":"2018-05-02T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"佢有條友出過本書 叫 致命中國"},{"pid":"08e66455c3c747794e7a304adda664cbc5500686","tid":649961,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"美國想改貿易逆差，無1000億根本唔收貨<br />\n<br />\n話之你點改革，美國而家劈頭就係要改現在貿易模式<br />\n<br />\n中國自己提的汽車，金融改革同貿易逆差無幫助，美國唔會收貨。<br />\n<br />\n再加埋301， 中興呢兩壇新野，中國呢次肯定要係入口關稅跪低<br />\n<br />\n牛肉，大豆，棉花，粟米，重工機械，天然氣，呢堆隨時會係呢次開會減關稅～<br />\n<br />\n中國如果企硬，到時無晒晶片入口，升級轉型失敗唔知會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2472500ba97afead06456e410443e2b44f37b197","tid":649961,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T05:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c1771cd4f40592ad3ba095fdcb66e53b9d46b6","tid":649961,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:52:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba96305c3074d386c9243bdb5384a1820684c419","tid":649961,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"成日吹到支那 咁撚高深<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心諗班人 根本唔知中國自古至今 成日輸<br />\n<br />\n唐朝長安起碼四次比人攻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宋朝 明朝 更被外族消滅"},{"pid":"82edebb3743bf63def798f2ff1da1790e66b0126","tid":649961,"uid":182475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"屌你台灣狗，根本係人地彭博早兩日篇opinion article成篇譯完當自己寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cb9b4477171a4117d4ac262e277b653114a4e1","tid":649961,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ceacc3fa1986e8db0f0c1e7a119694b133a1e68","tid":649961,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"